# ── Internal — not published to the public repo ───────────────────────────
# Brand system (shared across the plotplot garden)
.brand/
# Working/research docs — product docs (docs/*.md) and the tend map (docs/tend/) stay tracked
docs/ideas/
docs/research/
docs/plans/
docs/copeca-build-workflow.md
docs/tend-feedback.md

# ── Personal benchmarking config — run-specs + tool-under-test modes (not the tool) ──
# Scenarios are your experiment run-specs (like results/); keep example.yaml as the template.
/scenarios/*.yaml
!/scenarios/example.yaml
# Modes: the 5 generic A/B primitives stay tracked (they're the tool); tool-under-test modes are personal.
src/copeca/data/defaults/modes/*.yaml
!src/copeca/data/defaults/modes/baseline.yaml
!src/copeca/data/defaults/modes/hook.yaml
!src/copeca/data/defaults/modes/indexed.yaml
!src/copeca/data/defaults/modes/proxy.yaml
!src/copeca/data/defaults/modes/wrapper.yaml
